    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46336</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_202_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Rody&gt;さん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ms. &lt;Rody&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46460</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_202_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ヒマワリというのは、太陽に向かって
顔を上げているから美しいのです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>They say sunflowers are beautiful because they
always kept facing the sun.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46596</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_202_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>今のあなたは、雨の日のヒマワリのように、
あの美しさの全てを失ってしまっている</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You are like a sunflower under a rainy day,
whose beauty has long been lost.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46744</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_202_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Rody&gt;さん、ヒマワリには太陽が必要なのです。
私のように熱いハートを持った、灼熱の太陽が</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A sunflower needs the sun, Ms. &lt;Rody&gt;.
Allow my passionate heart become your burning sun.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46816</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_202_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>………………う……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ugh...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46888</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_202_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……く…………ぶふっ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Guh...Buu...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47032</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_202_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あっははははは！　ダメ、ダメだってぇ～～～！
あは、あは、はははははは！　ひー、ひー、苦しい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Bwaahahahah! I can't! I really can't!
Ahahahaha! Th-This is...so lame!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47124</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_202_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>な、なにを、そんなに笑ってる、だか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I-Is something funny?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47272</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_202_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だは、だ、だって、全然似合って、ない、あはは！
もうツボ、その喋り方、ツボすぎる！　ぎゃはは～</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>B-B-Because! Ahihihi...Th-The way you spoke
doesn't suit you at all! It's so sappy! Too sappy!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47364</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_006_202_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>作戦失敗だど……策士、策に溺れた……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>My strat...my strat didn't work...? My strat...
Gonna go sulk now.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>DEFINTIELY CAN BE WORDED BETTER</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
